<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
  <body>
    <table border="1px" width="700" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
      <tr>
        <td height="20" width="350"> SOS Cloud App</td>
        <td height="20" width="350"><b>Service Order: <%= @service_order.id %> </b></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
      <table border="1px" width="700" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <td height="20" width="80">Cliente: </td>
        <td height="20" width="620"><%= @service_order.client.name %></td>
      </table>
      <table border="1px" width="700" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <tr>
          <td height="20" width="80">Modulo:</td>
          <td height="20" width="270"><%= @service_order.module %></td>
          <td height="20" width="50">Motivo:</td>
          <td height="20" width="300"><%= @service_order.reason %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td height="20" width="80">Projeto:</td>
          <td height="20" width="270"><%= @service_order.project %></td>
          <td height="20" width="50">Solicitante:</td>
          <td height="20" width="300"><%= @service_order.requestor %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>

    <table border="1px" width="700" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
      <tr>
        <td height="20" width="80">Data:</td>
        <td height="20" width="140"><%= @service_order.date.strftime("%d/%m/%y") %></td>
        <td height="20" width="80">Inicio:</td>
        <td height="20" width="140"><%= @service_order.start_time %></td>
        <td height="20" width="80">Outros (+):</td>
        <td height="20" width="180"><%= @service_order.other_billable_hours %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td height="20" width="80">Analista:</td>
        <td height="20" width="140"><%= @service_order.user.name %></td>
        <td height="20" width="80">Fim:</td>
        <td height="20" width="140"><%= @service_order.end_time %></td>
        <td height="20" width="80">Outros (-):</td>
        <td height="20" width="180"><%= @service_order.non_billable_hours %></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
      <table border="1px" width="700" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <td height="20" width="80" >Total:</td>
        <td height="20" width="620"> <%= @service_order.total_time %> </td>
      </table>
    </table>
    <table border="1px" width="700" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
      <tr>
        <td height="20" width="700">Atividades:</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td height="20" width="700"><%= raw@service_order.description.gsub(/\n/, "<br>") %>
          <br>
          <br>
        </td>
      </tr>  
    </table>

    <table border="1px" width="700" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
      <tr>
        <td height="20" width="700">Observa&ccedil;&otilde;es:</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td height="20" width="700">
          <%= raw@service_order.comment.gsub(/\n/, "<br>") %>
          <br>
          <br>
        </td>
      </tr>  
    </table>
    <table border="1px" width="700" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
      <tr>
        <td>
          N&atilde;o h&aacute; restri&ccedil;&otilde;es e/ou observa&ccedil;&otilde;es sobre dados contidos nesta Ordem de Servi&ccedil;o. Alertamos que caso o 
          cliente n&atilde;o 
          se pronuncie, concordando ou n&atilde;o com o exposto, no prazo de 48 horas da data da emiss&atilde;o desta, seja via telefone, fax ou e-mail, perder&aacute; o direito de reclama&ccedil;&atilde;o.
          <br>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>